{
  "texts": [
    "Managing these complex models also needs specialized technical skills, which are not always available in public health settings.",
    "Language barriers are another important issue.",
    "Most sentiment analysis tools, datasets, and research focus mainly on English (35).",
    "Developing and testing methods for other languages, especially low-resource languages or languages from different cultural backgrounds, requires extra effort and resources (35, 54).",
    "Evaluating the performance and validity of sentiment analysis models carefully is a critical but often overlooked task in public health research."
  ]
}